## üóìÔ∏è Release Timeline

## Q1 2025 (January - March)

### Release v2.5 - Enhanced Detection

**Focus**: Detection engineering and threat hunting capabilities

#### High Priority Features

- [ ] **YARA Integration Module**
  - Scan memory dumps with YARA rules
  - Scan file system for malware signatures
  - Import custom YARA rule sets
  - Export YARA match results to CSV
  - Integration with common YARA rule repositories

- [ ] **Sigma Rule Detection**
  - Convert Sigma rules to PowerShell detection logic
  - Scan Windows Event Logs with Sigma rules
  - Support for common Sigma rule backends
  - Export detections with context and evidence

- [ ] **Enhanced Logging Framework**
  - Structured logging (JSON format)
  - Configurable log levels (Debug, Info, Warn, Error)
  - Separate log files for different script modules
  - Log rotation and retention policies

- [ ] **Improved Error Handling**
  - Graceful degradation for permission errors
  - Retry logic for transient failures
  - Detailed error messages with remediation steps
  - Error summary report at script completion

#### Medium Priority Features

- [ ] **Memory Artifact Collection**
  - Integration with WinPmem for memory acquisition
  - Process memory dumping capabilities
  - Memory strings extraction
  - Automated memory analysis hooks

- [ ] **Timeline Generation**
  - Automated timeline from collected artifacts
  - MACB (Modified, Accessed, Changed, Born) timeline
  - Super timeline format support
  - Export to Plaso/timesketch format

- [ ] **Configuration File Support**
  - YAML/JSON configuration files
  - Customizable artifact collection profiles
  - Pre-defined profiles (quick, standard, comprehensive)
  - Organization-specific configurations

#### Documentation

- [ ] Video tutorials for common scenarios
- [ ] Integration guides for popular SIEM platforms
- [ ] Threat hunting playbooks using the toolkit
- [ ] Performance tuning guide

---

## Q2 2025 (April - June)

### Release v3.0 - Advanced Analysis & Automation

**Focus**: Automated analysis and intelligence integration

#### High Priority Features

- [ ] **Automated IOC Extraction**
  - Extract IPs, domains, file hashes from artifacts
  - Automatic deduplication and formatting
  - Export in STIX/TAXII format
  - Integration with threat intelligence platforms

- [ ] **VirusTotal Integration**
  - Hash lookup for collected executables
  - Domain/IP reputation checking
  - Automated submission of suspicious files
  - Results correlation with collected artifacts

- [ ] **MITRE ATT&CK Mapping**
  - Map detected artifacts to ATT&CK techniques
  - Generate ATT&CK Navigator layers
  - TTP (Tactics, Techniques, Procedures) summary
  - Coverage heat maps

- [ ] **Automated Triage Scoring**
  - Risk scoring for collected artifacts
  - Suspicious activity ranking
  - Priority recommendations for analysts
  - Customizable scoring rules

#### Medium Priority Features

- [ ] **Registry Deep Dive**
  - Complete registry hive extraction
  - ShimCache analysis
  - AmCache parsing
  - UserAssist analysis
  - Recent document tracking

- [ ] **Prefetch Analysis**
  - Prefetch file parsing
  - Application execution timeline
  - File access patterns
  - Cross-reference with process artifacts

- [ ] **Event Log Enhanced Parsing**
  - XML event log parsing
  - Common attack pattern detection
  - Event correlation across sources
  - Suspicious event highlighting

- [ ] **Network Traffic Analysis Hooks**
  - Integration with network capture tools
  - PCAP file collection triggers
  - Network connection correlation
  - DNS query analysis enhancement

#### Documentation

- [ ] Advanced analysis techniques guide
- [ ] Threat intelligence integration examples
- [ ] MITRE ATT&CK hunting scenarios
- [ ] API integration documentation

---

## Q3 2025 (July - September)

### Release v3.5 - Enterprise & Cloud Integration

**Focus**: Enterprise deployment and cloud platform support

#### High Priority Features

- [ ] **Bulk Deployment Capabilities**
  - PowerShell DSC configurations
  - Group Policy deployment templates
  - SCCM/Intune deployment packages
  - Ansible playbook integration

- [ ] **Azure Sentinel Native Integration**
  - Direct upload to Log Analytics workspace
  - Custom table creation
  - Built-in KQL queries and workbooks
  - Automated alert rules

- [ ] **Cloud Artifact Collection**
  - Azure AD sign-in logs
  - Office 365 audit logs
  - Azure Activity logs
  - AWS CloudTrail integration (PowerShell Core)

- [ ] **Remote Execution Framework**
  - WinRM-based remote collection
  - PowerShell remoting optimization
  - Parallel execution across endpoints
  - Centralized result aggregation

#### Medium Priority Features

- [ ] **Compliance Reporting**
  - CIS benchmark checks
  - NIST CSF alignment
  - PCI DSS artifact collection
  - SOC 2 audit support

- [ ] **Custom Plugin Architecture**
  - Plugin development framework
  - Community plugin marketplace
  - Plugin manager (install/update/remove)
  - API for plugin development

- [ ] **Web-Based Reporting Dashboard**
  - HTML dashboard generation
  - Interactive charts and graphs
  - Executive summary reports
  - Technical detail views

- [ ] **Encrypted Evidence Storage**
  - Built-in AES encryption for artifacts
  - Password-protected ZIP archives
  - Certificate-based encryption
  - Secure key management

#### Documentation

- [ ] Enterprise deployment guide
- [ ] Cloud integration tutorials
- [ ] Compliance mapping documentation
- [ ] Plugin development guide

---

## Q4 2025 (October - December)

### Release v4.0 - AI-Assisted Analysis & Advanced Forensics

**Focus**: Machine learning and advanced forensic capabilities

#### High Priority Features

- [ ] **AI-Powered Anomaly Detection**
  - Baseline normal behavior
  - Detect statistical outliers
  - Machine learning model integration
  - Automated alert generation for anomalies

- [ ] **Natural Language Incident Reporting**
  - AI-generated incident summaries
  - Evidence correlation narratives
  - Timeline descriptions
  - Suggested next steps for analysts

- [ ] **Advanced File System Forensics**
  - MFT (Master File Table) parsing
  - USN Journal analysis
  - File slack space analysis
  - Deleted file recovery

- [ ] **Advanced Process Analysis**
  - Process tree visualization
  - DLL injection detection
  - Process hollowing identification
  - Reflective DLL loading detection

#### Medium Priority Features

- [ ] **Malware Analysis Sandbox Integration**
  - Automated submission to sandbox
  - Results retrieval and correlation
  - Behavioral analysis reports
  - Integration with Cuckoo, Joe Sandbox, etc.

- [ ] **Email Forensics Module**
  - PST/OST file parsing
  - Email header analysis
  - Attachment extraction and analysis
  - Phishing indicator detection

- [ ] **Mobile Device Triage**
  - iOS backup analysis (when connected)
  - Android device data extraction
  - Mobile app artifact collection
  - Cross-platform correlation

- [ ] **Cryptocurrency Forensics**
  - Wallet detection
  - Transaction history collection
  - Blockchain analysis integration
  - Ransomware payment tracking

#### Documentation

- [ ] AI-assisted analysis guide
- [ ] Advanced forensics techniques
- [ ] Case study collection
- [ ] Research paper contributions

