  - Unified cross-platform reporting

- [ ] **Real-Time Monitoring Mode**
  - Continuous artifact collection
  - Real-time threat detection
  - Event-driven response actions
  - Integration with EDR platforms

- [ ] **Graph Database Integration**
  - Neo4j for relationship mapping
  - Attack path visualization
  - Lateral movement detection
  - Entity relationship analysis

- [ ] **Kubernetes Forensics**
  - Container artifact collection
  - Pod memory dumps
  - Kubernetes audit log analysis
  - Container image analysis

- [ ] **Threat Intelligence Sharing**
